            "title": "遊台注意︱台東5.7級淺層地震  福建多地民眾感震動",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"台東下午1時許發生5.7級淺層地震，福建有民眾也感到震動。台灣中央氣象署\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e750688849379d255e38c178fce68228/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031314425410874.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">台東下午1時許發生5.7級淺層地震，福建有民眾也感到震動。台灣中央氣象署</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>台灣台東下午1時09分，發生極淺層5.7級地震，全台有震感之外，大陸的福建福州、泉州和莆田亦有民眾表示感到震動。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3436202/311%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%8714%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E5%8D%83%E5%B3%B6%E6%B5%B7%E6%BA%9D%E6%AD%A3%E7%B4%AF%E7%A9%8D%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%96%E5%BC%959%E7%B4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87\">311大地震14周年︱北海道千島海溝正累積能量 專家：或引9級地震</a>\n</p>\n<p>據台媒引述台灣中央氣象署資料顯示，是次地震震央位於臺東縣政府東北方 53.0 公里 ，位於台灣東部海域，地震深度12.5公里，黎克特制5.7級。全台均感受到明顯震動。暫未有傷亡報告。\n\n</p>\n<p>大陸福建有網民表示，在福州、泉州和莆田等地也有震感。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p><div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_box\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" is_mini=\"true\" style=\"background: initial !important; border: initial !important; border-radius: initial !important; border-spacing: initial !important; border-collapse: initial !important; direction: ltr !important; flex-direction: initial !important; font-weight: initial !important; height: initial !important; letter-spacing: initial !important; min-width: initial !important; max-width: initial !important; min-height: initial !important; max-height: initial !important; margin: auto !important; outline: initial !important; padding: initial !important; position: absolute; table-layout: initial !important; text-align: initial !important; text-shadow: initial !important; width: initial !important; word-break: initial !important; word-spacing: initial !important; overflow-wrap: initial !important; box-sizing: initial !important; display: initial !important; color: inherit !important; font-size: 13px !important; font-family: X-LocaleSpecific, sans-serif, Tahoma, Helvetica !important; line-height: 13px !important; vertical-align: top !important; white-space: inherit !important; left: 550px; top: 66px; opacity: 0.2;\">\n<div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_logo\" title=\"翻譯選取的文字\"> </div>\n<div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_sound\" title=\"朗讀\" title_play=\"朗讀\" title_stop=\"停止\"> </div>\n<div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_copy\" title=\"將文字複製到剪貼簿\"> </div>\n</div>\n<link href=\"moz-extension://e5e0c8cc-d50e-4025-a617-4623c74b4c06/skin/s3gt_tooltip_mini.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\"/>\n<style media=\"print\" type=\"text/css\">\n\n#s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini { display: none !important; }\n\n\n</style>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
