            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "有片│ 中環嘉咸街私家車逆駕  網民：咁都得？",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/a0728cd6ffca71efbfbf4177d1c10102/a69a4971b5ba405d90a734ae858d4d35-fdac6922351e68fc75badbd25c82f82e-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d27c2d6fec8\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d27c2d6feca\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ebac859e1a38bea2d3a2079410a6d27a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031314251712893.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中環打卡熱點的中環壁畫走廊嘉咸街，平日人山人海，前（11）日發生逆駕事件，一輛私家車逆駕落斜，險與一輛上斜私家車發生相撞，逆駕司機知衰剷上行人路，讓上斜私家車緩緩而過，網民直斥離譜：「日光日白都咁樣」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134656/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車沿荷李活道轉入嘉咸街。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0004e570e1fbaf0373fda780d338b74e/2025-03/01_6.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車沿荷李活道轉入嘉咸街。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134657/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車沿荷李活道轉入嘉咸街。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/894384286637b4665a7e1e760481ecbe/2025-03/02_6.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車沿荷李活道轉入嘉咸街。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134658/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛私家車逆線而下。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/410b74888b8d6dd9577192c84abdc695/2025-03/03_8.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛私家車逆線而下。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134659/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛私家車逆線而下。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d1f117ba05796ac58a44f2e32ae51f0/2025-03/04_7.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛私家車逆線而下。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134660/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛私家車逆線而下。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cf32f0d986e54704ecfa4ce24d186ddf/2025-03/05_7.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛私家車逆線而下。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134661/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"逆駕私家車剷上行人路讓路。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fa5a03f9f558d29b5e73f520ac950fa7/2025-03/06_6.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        逆駕私家車剷上行人路讓路。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134662/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"逆駕私家車剷上行人路讓路。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9daf3472fdff31f801d93f0706b97b86/2025-03/07_4.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        逆駕私家車剷上行人路讓路。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134663/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"逆駕私家車剷上行人路讓路。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c82d22c6f868fdd4b0ebca7907d203d/2025-03/08_3.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        逆駕私家車剷上行人路讓路。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>片段全長一分鐘，片中一輛私家車沿荷李活道右轉上嘉咸街，該段單線單程，准上不准落，豈料一輛私家車沿嘉咸街而下，雙方立時剎車，未致釀成意外，逆駕私家車緩緩剷上行人路讓路，讓上斜私家車離去，片段結束。\n\n</p>\n<p>網民表示：「下（吓），咁都得？」、「 逆線已經夠衰，仲要剷埋上行人路」、「希望片主唔好嫌麻煩，一定要作出投訴，危險駕駛者一個都不能放過。」、「佢呢類司機需要有D教訓」。\n\n</p>\n<p>嘉咸街壁畫近年成為中環打卡熱點，斜坡上的巨型壁畫出自本地塗鴉藝術家Alex Croft之手，他受到昔日九龍城寨啟發，以鮮藍色背景配上色彩繽紛的唐樓，形成鮮明對比，生動地重現老香港的韻味和風貌，馳名中外，成為中環最具人氣的打卡熱點之一。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
