        {
            "title": "歐聯｜多蒙特淘汰里爾 射手古拉斯平沙拿神級紀錄 8強硬撼巴塞隆拿",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"多蒙特射手古拉斯(右)。AFP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/46ba65de1049928d7475f5b38feda594/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031313363857597.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">多蒙特射手古拉斯(右)。AFP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>多蒙特射手古拉斯於於周三歐聯16強次回合交出一次助攻後，今季歐聯已炮製14個入球，追平利物浦球星穆罕默德沙拿的紀錄，並列單季貢獻最多歐聯入球的非洲球員，終助球隊作客2:1擊敗里爾，兩回合計贏3:2晉級8強將硬撼巴塞隆拿，主帥尼高高華即表示會嚴陣以待。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特射手古拉斯(左)。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c233372f04c2055ded400feca407209f/2025-03/AFP__20250312__36ZY4QT__v1__HighRes__FblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特射手古拉斯(左)。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特射手古拉斯(右)。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7b48ee37a6d9577a749f67eb2d1043b/2025-03/AFP__20250312__37229EN__v1__HighRes__FblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特射手古拉斯(右)。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc7d4bb7790e6d0ae91411868f5ed7c6/2025-03/AFP__20250312__37227E9__v4__HighRes__FblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c33fe5c19ba763bd7c68890903b6d04a/2025-03/AFP__20250312__37229E6__v2__HighRes__TopshotFblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f8aa6446541a2c9a60db4792e248ffb/2025-03/AFP__20250312__36ZZ7TH__v4__HighRes__FblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安利簡恩射入12碼。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7eaf7ac3cc8dbcb3dcefb348c028707/2025-03/AFP__20250312__37232GP__v1__HighRes__FblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安利簡恩射入12碼。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49c6bc6f0881b11dc1c860e0883d64cb/2025-03/AFP__20250312__372367Z__v2__HighRes__FblEurC1LilleDortmund.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特淘汰里爾晉級。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>古拉斯平沙拿紀錄</h2>\n<p>古拉斯今季加盟多蒙特後表現神勇，尤其於歐聯上陣12場共入10球，於射手榜排並列第2位。今場他亦有貢獻，於下半場助攻麥斯比亞射入奠勝一球，助球隊作客2:1反勝里爾，兩回合計贏3:2晉級8強。連同今仗，這名幾內亞射手今季歐聯同時收穫4次助攻，個人合共炮製14個入球，追平沙拿的紀錄，，並列單季貢獻最多歐聯入球的非洲球員，並有機會於8強挑戰破紀錄。\n\n</p><h2>8強大戰巴塞隆拿</h2>\n<p>蜜蜂軍團晉級後將與巴塞隆拿爭入4強，強敵當前全隊都嚴陣以待，主帥尼高高華表示：「眾將表現出色，尤其在先落後下反勝，證明了球隊的質素。里爾擅長控球在腳，但巴塞更勝一籌。因此，我們屆時需要充分利用控球的機會，用速度傷害對手。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
